{"tid":1884144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國政府將協助宣傳「中共」監控品牌","createTime":"2020-02-17T12:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:22:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"074f89cb0208321c57354720bf112610ac52fa56","tid":1884144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"「海康威視」向中共提供監控系統. &nbsp;美國政府早已因此決定制裁海康威視<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1638162/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1638162/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過, 英國政府已決定協助宣傳「海康威視」<br />\n英國政府將在3月舉辦安全和治安展覽, 政府已決定容許「海康威視」參與這個展覽.<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨議員Bob Seely表示希望英國政府可收回成命, 更直言英國不能再為了討好中共而&quot;漠視道德&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/feb/17/uk-to-promote-chinese-firm-hikvision-implicated-in-uighur-rights-abuses?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;CMP=twt_gu&amp;utm_medium=&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1581935237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2020%2Ffeb%2F17%2Fuk-to-promote-chinese-firm-hikvision-implicated-in-uighur-rights-abuses%3Futm_term%3DAutofeed%26CMP%3Dtwt_gu%26utm_medium%3D%26utm_source%3DTwitter%23Echobox%3D1581935237&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=4826c639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/feb/17/uk-to-promote-chinese-firm-hikvision-implicated-in-uighur-rights-abuses?utm_term=Autofeed&amp;CMP=twt_gu&amp;utm_medium=&amp;utm_source=Twitter#Echobox=1581935237</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>UK to promote Chinese firm 'implicated' in Uighur rights abuses</strong><br />\nGovernment to host Hikvision surveillance firm accused of threatening human rights<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The UK government is to promote a Chinese surveillance company that has been blacklisted by the US after it was &ldquo;implicated&rdquo; in human rights violations of the country&rsquo;s Uighur Muslim minority.</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe Home Office has agreed to allow <strong>Hikvision, a surveillance equipment provider active in China&rsquo;s western Xinjiang province</strong>, to attend the Security and Policing trade fair it is hosting in Farnborough in March.<br />\n<br />\nA Conservative backbencher called on government departments to rethink the invitation, which comes a few months after the Trump administration accused Hikvision of helping with &ldquo;high-technology surveillance against Uighurs&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nHikvision was one of nine companies due to attend the event that had been accused of threatening human rights, according to an analysis of the 300 companies listed to attend, conducted by the internet research company Top10VPN and shared with the Guardian.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>The Tory MP Bob Seely said he hoped the Home Office would reconsider the invitation. &ldquo;We need to stop having an ethical bypass when it comes to China and hi-tech. If we are going to proclaim UK values and standards, we need at least the appearance of consistency.&rdquo;</strong>"},{"pid":"462c2f16592985bf0d4081a7deeb14d5f0a26e03","tid":1884144,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"脫歐親共? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e61c3054b4690a069fdb4fb3b38ec6d6a80a40","tid":1884144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a1a034f5e1ada6cd15a5542f82aad9f8f37160","tid":1884144,"uid":173191,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日落帝國</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"baea41005000eb74144c72620972d0adea203dd8","tid":1884144,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f9a1a034f5e1ada6cd15a5542f82aad9f8f37160","tid":1884144,"uid":173191,"like":